t-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe99018c-7b46-47b2-be33-dc56b7ee882a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e12fa336-6c7f-469c-b212-7d9ffef7c197\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기존의 디자인이 아닌 것으로도 작업이 가능한가요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69d14546-02ee-4be1-a7b0-e0b7b986a0e6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a354caa3-1331-4d78-b2ba-3f2a26f29825\" style=\"color:#555555;\">당연히 새로운 디자인으로 작업이 가능합니다. 다만 자료와 비용 기간이 추가될 수 있습니다. 하지만 내용에 따라 금액이 변경될 수 있지만 큰 비용이 청구되지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-463a5915-8c45-4ae6-bbfd-381f8878055d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d03d6278-44ec-40c7-8480-0bc96133fea6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-406034d3-f735-4674-9a06-df8a46f6fe68\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223101107483/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d6d55f9c-0cff-4cc4-a98e-a4eeb6550d13\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-863f7d70-fbb2-469a-8d6a-476362000dd9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a101a3d2-895e-4c3a-a056-1301d7efe5a6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로고나 사진 보정을 진행하여 이미지로 작업하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07c1c13a-809b-496c-94e4-954c156b4b6e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a6b3dd4c-7de3-43aa-8cd7-3f58764523a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사진을 카테고리별로 깔끔하게 삽입하고 일반적인 디자인 형식으로 진행하였습니다. 꽃 분위기에 맞는 화사한 색감을 추구하여 기존의 템플릿 색상과는 다르게 작업하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be16afc1-b8a2-485d-84a0-be79d00ee6d6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8cdfaff5-3750-4e31-86b0-7aa291d59908\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b8127771-defe-458f-9768-37907d494f0e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-aebe3dcf-5da1-4cd6-8f8a-9de89bfa6455\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 프로필명함이 궁금하신 분은 언제든지 문의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d2510f36-013e-4d9d-9e2a-a26842d54346\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-da98f7d1-dfe4-4bd3-a164-3b5794ade15e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc0a6415-fa29-44ac-b427-18fea28c5412\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-03fbe687-9047-4bf1-ab29-26fe2c8a8e26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
